originalText.text: Melissa has changed my life in the months we have been working together, and she continues to in every session. It was hard to find a therapist who can help with working through deep rooted past issues, as well as create practical strategies for present issues. Melissa is that and more, she is kind and patient and I look forward to our sessions like a breath of fresh air.  I cannot recommend her enough to anyone looking for someone with her specialties / focus.
